			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Speak to Phoenix Lubbins - S_GLO_IronThrone_Group2_Prisoner1 aede3e82-f02b-4d6c-a92f-e9418b1b0e37 - (39; 39; 67)  in the Dock warehouse after saving them.\r\n\r\nQuick setup:\r\n- Load CTY_Main_A\r\n- Use Debug Book (Ctrl + Shift + 9)\r\n- Set Quest Flags and Options -> Act3 (LOW) -> Iron Throne -> Change State -> Back At Docks -> MajoritySaved\r\n- Then talk to the NPC"
				},
